F \wedge (F\vee q) = F
 \begin{align*}  p\wedge (p\vee q)&\equiv (p\wedge p)\vee(p\wedge q)\ - \ Distributive \ law\\ &\equiv p\vee(p\wedge q) \ - \ Idempotent \ law\\ &\equiv p \ - \ Absorption \ law \end{align*} 
(p ∧ (p ∨ q)) ⇔ (p ∧ (p ∨ q)) ∨ (p ∧ ¬p) ⇔ (p ∧ ((p ∨ q) ∨ ¬p)) ⇔ p
